{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require Student Loans Company to automatically refund overpayments",
        "additional_details": "Many people in the UK have been unintentionally overpaying their student loan amounts. We believe that the SLC have not been sufficiently proactive in returning overpayments, nor appropriately responsive when they have been contacted by the customer.\r\n \r\nWe believe this approach is unethical and should be challenged.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should require the SLC to issue refunds automatically for all unintentional overpayments, similar to tax, without the payer having to request it. ",
